该站是2号线首个安装升降平台的车站。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bj.xinhuanet.com/bjpd-zhuanti/2008-02/26/content_12541051.htm|title=东四十条站率先安装升降平台 便于残疾人进出地铁站|publisher=[[北京娱乐信报|北京娱乐信报]]|date=2008-02-26|accessdate=2015-04-14|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923191611/http://www.bj.xinhuanet.com/bjpd-zhuanti/2008-02/26/content_12541051.htm|archivedate=2015-09-23}}</ref>

